      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is an FDA-recognized simulation software with published V&V documentation. The custom Python module is under version control (tag v2.3.1) and unit tests achieve 87% line coverage for the hemolysis integration kernel. SQA documentation reviewed and deemed adequate for MRL 2. No runtime exception testing or fault-injection testing was performed on the solver or post-processing pipeline; all SQA evidence derives from nominal execution logs and static code review."
