    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error GCI = 3.2% is within the 5% criterion. Output comparison MAE = 9.3% is within the 15% criterion. The single solver restart event was documented and resolved; all production runs completed nominally with converged residuals. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis model provides adequate credibility to support the regulatory decision that RH < 1 for the worst-case operating conditions of the Class II CPB device.",
